body.raw: George Brown is a trailblazer in the field of intellectual property law, specializing in patents, trademarks, and copyright matters. A graduate of Yale Law School, she combines her legal expertise with a deep understanding of technology and innovation. Sophia has successfully represented startups, tech giants, and creative individuals in safeguarding their intellectual assets and resolving disputes in rapidly evolving industries.
